title: Libya - How Did We Get Here? Part 3
itunes:title: Libya - How Did We Get Here? Part 3
description:
We wrap up this short history with Shereen explaining the most recent and seemingly never-ending election process in Libya, and how current prime minister Abdul Hamid Dbeibeh has been able to forcefully stay in power.
